summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; accepting quit claim deeds to certain real property located in the Southwest quarter of Section 11 and the Southwest quarter of Section 15, Township 21 North, Range 10 East, W.M.; in the Northeast quarter of Section 29, Township 22 North, Range 10 East, W.M.; and in the Southeast quarter of Section 29, Township 22 North, Range 10 East, W.M.; all situate in King County, Washington.
